{
  "title": "Smoky Savory Australian Salmon Skewers",
  "description": "A briny and molten Australian dish featuring salmon, this recipe is perfect for a special occasion, with a cure that adds a smoky flavor and a shojin-friendly twist that makes it accessible to all, showcasing the unique flavors of Australia",
  "cuisine": "Australian",
  "diet": [
